&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Previous applicants need not apply&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consultant Dermatologist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6-10 PA’s (negotiable)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Dermatology Service is looking for a enthusiastic and innovative professionals to complement the current clinical team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are commissioned to provide a wide range of dermatology services to our local communities within Hampshire, Surrey and Berkshire. Our services include minor operations, skin cancer, vulval, patch testing, phototherapy, psoriasis, dermatopathology and general dermatology. The successful applicants will be required to participate and deliver as many of these services as appropriate. Any cases requiring input from our colleagues in other specialties i.e. general surgery, ENT, plastics are managed in house through internal referrals. Sub speciality interests which complement the existing team would be advantageous, but not essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a negotiable established post (6-10 Pa’s) to enhance the care of our dermatology patients within the clinic and minor operations environments, and also on the hospital wards. You will assist the consultant team, specialty doctors and specialist nurses to provide a service that meets the needs of our ever expanding caseload. Attendance at local and network multidisciplinary team (MDT) meetings and local team meetings will be expected.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should possess Membership of the Royal College of Physicians (MRCP) and have a wealth of prior experience in dermatology. The ability to drive will be essential due to the number of off-site clinics we run; we can provide an electric car if necessary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So if you’re looking for a fantastic place to work and you share our values of being committed to excellence, working together and facing the future, then please apply now.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information or to come and visit our unit, please contact&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Alia Ahmed,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Consultant Dermatologist on : 0300  615 3108&lt;/p&gt;
